column5: If any body has any imfomation about Ogani lake(amounts of fish, what the fishing is like in mid july) I would be greatful.
We fished that lake a couple of years ago(5 of us) and we caught somewhere in the neighborhood of 5000 fish. I would recomend that lake to anyone who really wants to catch alot of walleyes.
Where exactly is Ogani lake and what outfitter did you book with?
